data.description: Nestled on a sprawling 2.44-acre oasis, this equestrian property is a dream come true for horse lovers and those seeking a serene countryside lifestyle. Step into your very own slice of heaven, featuring a delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom main house spanning 1,559 square feet, and an additional 764 square feet of comfort in the charming split-level guest house, boasting 3 bedrooms and 1 bathroom. Whether you're looking to accommodate guests or generate rental income, The possibilities are endless! For those passionate about horses, this property offers a haven for both you and your equine companions. The corals and horse setup provide ample space for your beloved horses to graze and roam freely. It offers the perfect balance between rural serenity and suburban convenience.
